2
00:00:05.071 --> 00:00:07.874
How to order a replacement for a damaged card

3
00:00:08.441 --> 00:00:14.481
Start by clicking 'Report damaged, lost or stolen card'
from the quick links section

4
00:00:14.481 --> 00:00:17.083
or by going to the 'Manage accounts' tab.

5
00:00:17.083 --> 00:00:22.322
Then select 'Report a damaged, lost or stolen card'
from the 'Card servicesâ€™ section.

6
00:00:22.322 --> 00:00:24.924
Now select the account your card is on

7
00:00:25.225 --> 00:00:27.927
and the card that needs to be replaced.

8
00:00:27.927 --> 00:00:30.764
Then select 'My card is damaged'.

9
00:00:31.431 --> 00:00:33.166
Click 'Next'.

10
00:00:33.833 --> 00:00:36.369
Check your delivery address is correct.

11
00:00:36.636 --> 00:00:41.141
You'll be able to use your existing card
until your replacement card arrives.

12
00:00:41.141 --> 00:00:42.442
Click 'Next'.

13
00:00:42.442 --> 00:00:47.213
If the details are correct, click on
'Confirm new card order'.

14
00:00:47.514 --> 00:00:48.848
And you're done.

15
00:00:48.848 --> 00:00:53.253
Your new card is on its way and will
be with you within five working days.

16
00:00:53.253 --> 00:00:58.024
Replacing a damaged card made easy
with Barclays Online Banking.

